Piggies by the Beatles Have you seen the little piggies Crawling in the dirt? And for all the little piggies Life is getting worse Always having dirt to play around in Have you seen the bigger piggies In their starched white shirts? You will find the bigger piggies Stirring up the dirt Always have clean shirts to play around in In their styes with all their backing They don't care what goes on around In their eyes there's something lacking What they need's a damn good whacking Everywhere there's lots of piggies Living piggy lives You can see them out for dinner With their piggy wives Clutching forks and knives to eat their bacon [One more time...] WUUU!!! Wasn't that FUNNNN???? Yes. Yes it was. And what's even MORE funnier than the lyrics is the tune. xD Everytime I hear this song I can imagine GIR running into a field in slow mo, playing with his piggies. xD I dunno. I'm insane.

I feel a bit better...if not that maybe even more than a bit. I'm still upset over Havana though. No matter what, even if she hates me forever, I still consider her one of my best friends. And I care about her, even if she won't for me. That's what friendship is about. Right? So, I'm not angry at you Havana. I wished you could read this and understand. Please. We really need to talk. Hmmm...Easter was interesting. Parents got me the White Album from the Beatles. I have to say, this is one of the best C.D.s ever created. Its wonderful. :)

Hmm. I thought about cutting myself tonight. You know...trying out to see if Havana was right, that hurting yourself would stop the pain for a while anyway. After all...after what she said...me not being apart of her life anymore...it made me feel depressed. It seemed like the right idea at the time. But than, why?! Why would I do such a thing?!?! I have loved ones!! Though very few that I love...and less yet, ones that love me. Besides...I don't want to get in trouble with my parents. I don't even want to get in trouble with Chi. And I hate knifes or scissors!!! I hate anything sharp! I hate to bleed...and I hate pain. Especially in the heart...yet alone skin itself. I'm not a suicidal girl. Though people hate me, I don't care anymore. I shouldn't care. I should only care about the ones that love me. I'm never, ever going to think of the option of cutting myself ever again, I promise.

I've died once before...from another woman. Forget it...just get out of my life. Please. -Havana/Tinkerbell My Dad always said...that...when we fall in love with people...it is not our fault. We didn't decide to fall in love with them. Fate chose us to. When somebody can't forgive you for your actions, it is almost as if life was blind in the first place. I feel as if I've discovered that...I've been living lies of actions of what we humans chose and to. We can't control what our human minds command us to. I've not only lost a loved one for my chosen actions, but now a best friend...to even just a friend. I guess this means Havana and me are enemies now. I only wish that she'd know that this wasn't suppose to happen. But I can't lie. I am in love with Jasmine. I'm not sorry for that. So...Havana...I guess this is goodbye.

My emotion...it feels so odd. It dwells in my heart. It makes me smile. Yet makes me cry. I want to spell it out, but I can't. Its so...undescrible. 

If I say it...it could destroy something...but if I don't...it'll destroy me. Emotionally anyway. I might be driven insane by this. *sighs* 

Damn emotions get the best of me. No matter what I won't be able to let go. I just know it. 

All I can do is look up to the sky, gaze at the stars, and pray for answers. I can only wait for my wish to come true. Where is it? I hope its not to distant. I don't think I can wait any longer...

Of course...you always get the satsifaction that someday...another way or another, they'll realize that you did, you very much DID help them, and they never did say thanks. Things like that make me smile.
